<body onload="initialize()">
    <div class="col-xs-12 page-header">
    <%= image_tag("birminghamblight.jpg", class:"img-responsive", alt:"Responsive image") %>
    <h1>Report Some Blight Y'all</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="map col-xs-12">
    <h2>First things first, where's the blight at?</h2>
    <span>
      <button class="btn btn-primary">use my location</button>
      or
      <button class="btn btn-primary">just enter address</button>
    </span>
  </div>
  <div class="address col-xs-12">
  <div class="input-group" id="locationField">
    <span class="input-group-addon" id="basic-addon1">@</span>
    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="autocomplete" placeholder="Enter your address" onFocus="geolocate()" aria-describedby="basic-addon1">
  </div>
</div>

  <span>
    <h2>take some pictures</h2>
  </span>
  <div class="pictures jumbotron"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-camera" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
  <div class="row">
    <h3>what is the nature of the decay?</h3>
    <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-2">
      <a class="thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag("blight1.jpg", alt:"blight1") %>
      </a>
      <h3>bad</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-2">
      <a class="thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag("blight2.jpg", alt:"blight2") %>
<!--         <img src="images/blight2.jpg" alt="blight2"> -->
      </a>
      <h3>worse</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-2">
      <a class="thumbnail">
        <%= image_tag("blight3.jpg", alt:"blight3") %>
<!--         <img src="images/blight3.jpg" alt="blight3"> -->
      </a>
      <h3>terrible</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3>How big is the property</h3>
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <button type="button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">1 story</button>
        <button type="button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">2 story</button>
        <button type="button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">3 stories +</button>
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-xs-12">
    <h3>Give us a better idea of the property</h3>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
      <button id="PropBurn" type="PropDetails PropDetails_Burn button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">burn damage</button>
      <button id="PropOvergrown" type="PropDetails PropDetails_Overgrown button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">overgrown</button>
      <button id="PropShingles" type="PropDetails PropDetails_Shingles button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">missing shingles</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
          <button id="PropTrash" type="PropDetails PropDetails_Trash button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">trash</button>
          <button type="PropDetails PropDetails_Abandoned button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">abandoned cars</button>
          <button type="PropDetails PropDetails_Occupied button btn-lg" class="btn btn-default">occupied</button>
  </div>
</div>

    <div class="hidden overgrown col-xs-12">
      <h3>How Overgrown is the property?</h3>
      Some overgrowth
      <input id="overgrown" data-slider-id='OvergrownSlider' type="text" data-slider-min="0" data-slider-max="10" data-slider-step="1" data-slider-value="0" />Like a wild forest.
    </div>
    <div class="hidden burnt col-xs-12">
      <h3>how much burn damage is there?</h3>
      Some burn damage
      <input id="BurnSlider" data-slider-id='BurnSlider' type="text" data-slider-min="0" data-slider-max="10" data-slider-step="1" data-slider-value="0" />the 7th layer of hell.
    </div>
    <div class="hidden shingles col-xs-12">
      <h3>How many of the shingles are missing?</h3>
      <div class="col-xs-12">
      Some shingles
      <span id="shingle_1" class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span id="shingle_2" class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span id="shingle_3" class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span id="shingle_4"  class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span id="shingle_5" class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-down" aria-hidden="true"></span>
       there is no roof.
     </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hidden trash col-xs-12">
      <h3>How much trash is on the lot?</h3>
      Some trash
      <input id="trash" data-slider-id='TrashSlider' type="text" data-slider-min="0" data-slider-max="10" data-slider-step="1" data-slider-value="0" /> like the great pacific trashpile.
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h3>Any other details</h3>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="give additional details" aria-describedby="sizing-addon1">
    </div>
    <div id="hidden burnt Burnslider"></div>
</body>